      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/460549-h-ng-g-oli-ng-ji-z">Quotes from Red Sorghum</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;Finally, she mused that human existence is as brief as the life of autumn grass, so what was there to fear from taking chances with your life?&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
